title: Daumier Drawings (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Metropolitan | 1993 | 0810964236 | English | 280 pages | PDF | 43 MB

Daumier emerges as an artist of exceptional genius and modernity in this volume.

Honore Daumier's works. The three author- curators (and two contributors) have focused on the 19th-century caricaturist's less known drawings and watercolors, also using selected examples of his paintings, prints, and bronzes to illustrate the development of his style and his exploration of particular themes. A splendid celebration of an extraordinarily modern sensibility
